{"tid":1439961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"還原催淚彈過期既真相+文宣及未來方向","createTime":"2019-08-10T09:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T06:34:47.000Z","uid":152103,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"54d3d0538af21e5be4bbaf77ec44ca7181b105f9","tid":1439961,"uid":152103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:32:25.000Z","msg":"催淚彈過期既問題好似少少俾人忽略咗, 其重要性單單就安全性既問題不在話下<br />\n而更奇怪既係...點解狗隻記者會一而再, 再而三咁迴避呢個問題<br />\n因為跟據狗隻既手法, 佢一定會好禮義廉咁抵賴<br />\n由元朗39分鐘事件, 改裝警棍到雷射槍佢都好強詞奪理咁「解釋」<br />\n<br />\n但係今次ER....ER....我無資料<br />\n點解會咁? 因為佢根本<strong>拆唔到!</strong><br />\n<br />\n我雖極力隱藏，他們卻死纏不休。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GO2CEXf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGO2CEXf.jpg&h=fb12fcb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以我地更加要加大文宣力度<br />\n<br />\n以下係少少背景資料, 因為大部分都唔公開, 所以只可儘力還原<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3YBVx3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3YBVx3.jpg&h=3cb6d792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xAhi8TT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxAhi8TT.jpg&h=6ca2cc44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gd3RKsS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgd3RKsS.jpg&h=455c568a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y2KdXN5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy2KdXN5.jpg&h=a6e015cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCyKj1L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCyKj1L.jpg&h=f60226d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OGJqOU7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGJqOU7.jpg&h=bfe9b0fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MDEafAa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMDEafAa.jpg&h=ee028201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LfjafAc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLfjafAc.jpg&h=88afde3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GTpYptB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGTpYptB.jpg&h=affe048a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>集思廣益部分</strong><br />\n安全問題醫護界已經發表晒報告, 但報告始終從結果收集數據,<br />\n始終生產商既安全報告先最重要<br />\n其次希望可以收集多D既資訊, 例如: 分別邊年既過期催淚彈, 大約佔幾成, 警方點違反指引, 好似係射入民居, 中信大廈事件等等<br />\n<br />\n集合所有事實, 我已經搵到法律界朋友幫手發聯署信要求生產商公開佢手頭上資料, 要求重新審視同香港警方既合作關係"},{"pid":"3e5554a8b024ee5b641f9bda8dc1c6598f75c58d","tid":1439961,"uid":191733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:33:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7aabcfb95040d94d3b204ae0ef4d922a8b66b03e","tid":1439961,"uid":42360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:34:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc30e31ec8a9344c94e7805d4f9449a166d6a249","tid":1439961,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:36:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da40f2f120c8ef86ccd1944a29c7be865ee9a39f","tid":1439961,"uid":193204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ee16ecd787fdbc013702455c10acf7690c0eae","tid":1439961,"uid":152103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"4aae94cdf35a50fc081e04a1e3295f8451866ac6","tid":1439961,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6ac2efdd6b37505c52f89bbb60ffe1973ceecc","tid":1439961,"uid":152103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:50:34.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"9de4aac78d07e4533e67d72a539607fb28ac31ed","tid":1439961,"uid":36089,